sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Shopper
    participant App as Next.js App
    participant WA as Messenger/WhatsApp
    participant Sister as Sister (Seller)

    User->>App: Adds items to Cart
    User->>App: Clicks "Checkout"
    App->>App: Format Order Message\n(Items, Total, ID)
    App->>App: Generate Deep Link\n(wa.me or m.me)
    App->>WA: Redirects with pre-filled text
    User->>WA: Hits "Send"
    WA->>Sister: Delivers Message\n"Hi, buying: Item A..."
    Sister->>User: Replies with GCash QR / Total
    User->>Sister: Sends Payment Screenshot
    Sister->>Sister: Marks order complete (Manual)